<%= render 'shared/sub_nav' %>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-xs-1"></div>
  <div class="col-xs-10">
    <div class="profile-container">

      <p>Hello <%= current_user.full_name %> and welcome to your private Brighter Beginnings Adopt-a-Family account page. Come here to manage your personal information, acquire information about the famil(ies) you adopt each year, and even to remind yourself about when and where you've scheduled your gift drop off.</p>

      <p>Remember that you can receive a tax break for your gift donations. <%= link_to 'Download your tax receipt form here', download_pdf_path(:file => 'tax_receipt.pdf') %>.</p>
      
      <div class="col-sm-4 col-xs-12 column">
        <h2>Drop Location Details</h2>
        <% unless current_user.drop_location_id && current_user.drop_location_id != 0 || user_is_admin? %>
          <p>You haven't yet chosen your preferred drop location. You will need to do so before being able to view the families available for adoption. On the home page, just click on the 'Browse Families' button and you'll see a prompt to choose your location.</p>
        <% end %>

        <% if current_user.drop_location_id == 0 or user_is_super_admin? %>
          <p>As a super administrator on the site, you are not required to choose a drop location and will be able to view families from all locations at all times.</p>
        <% end %>


        <% if current_user.drop_location_id && current_user.drop_location_id != 0 %>
        <ul>
          <li><p><%= DropLocation.find(current_user.drop_location_id).name %></p></li>

          <li><p><%= DropLocation.find(current_user.drop_location_id).street %>, <%= DropLocation.find(current_user.drop_location_id).city %>, <%= DropLocation.find(current_user.drop_location_id).zipcode %></p></li>
          <% if user_is_a_donor?  %>
          <li><p><%= current_user.drop_date.date_and_time.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %l:%M %p') %></p></li>
          <% end %>

        </ul>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-4 col-xs-12 column">
        <h2>Contact Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <% if current_user.full_name != nil %>
            <li><p>Name: <%= current_user.full_name %><p></li>
          <% end %>
          
          <% if current_user.street != nil && current_user.state && current_user.zip %>
            <li><p>Address: <%= current_user.street %>, <%= current_user.city %>, <%= current_user.zip %>, <%= current_user.state %></p></li>
          <% end %>

          <% if current_user.phone != nil %>
            <li><p>Phone: <%= current_user.phone %></p></li>
          <% end %>


          <li><%= link_to 'Add or Edit Your Personal Info', edit_user_path(current_user) %></li>

        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-sm-3 col-xs-12 column">
        <h2>Adopted Families</h2>
        <% unless user_is_a_donor?  %>
          <p>No famlies adopted yet...</p>
        <% end %>

        <% if user_is_a_donor?  %>
        <ul>
          <% current_user.families.each do |f| %>
          <li>
            <ul class="col-lg-5">
              <li><p><%= link_to f.code, family_path(f) %></p></li>
            </ul>
            <% end %>
          </li>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <% end %>
    </div>


    
  </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
